hopobject.body: Children with disabilities quetiapine xr wikipedia Assistant Sheriff McDonald, who oversees the jail system, notes that the highest recidivism rates are among mentally ill inmates. Ms. McDonald is among several county officials pushing for a new jail facility designed specifically for mental-health and drug-abuse treatment. Such a project would cost between $1.3 billion and $1.6 billion, according to an independent study commissioned by the county.
